sellerAgent.name: Timothy Maciejewski - NY Licensed Assoc. R.E. Broker

data.description: This updated 1,700+ sq. ft., 4-bed, 2-bath farmhouse in the Eden School District is located on 20 Acres of land & is perfect for the outdoor/agricultural enthusiast! Tastefully remodeled and decorated, this home is move-in ready & includes a large barn, chicken coop & 3 car garage all with metal roofs. With plenty of spaces for entertaining, including a remodeled Kitchen (2022) w/butcher block countertops and newer appliances, a large Dining Room, spacious Living Room w/wood burning fireplace, a 3-season Amish built sunroom w/hot tub, fireplace, sun lights that leads to a huge 32x12 deck, this home does not disappoint. The 1st floor also boasts a full bedroom and bathroom w/walk-in bath & laundry room w/newer dryer & washer. The 2nd floor includes an updated Bath Fitter bathroom w/shower (2023), new wall to wall carpeting (2022) and 3 spacious bedrooms. Outside, enjoy the views from the large deck, hunt from the hunting sheds or enjoy the shade on the covered porch. Close to the I-90, this home is less than 30 minutes to downtown Buffalo or to Fredonia.  Don't miss the opportunity to make your farmhouse dream a reality!
